metadata.name: Landing
metadata.description:
The deepest shadow, the spark
And the reflection in the water.
No memories exist,
There're only wonders.

***

"The Gate" is a captivating journey into the depths of the human psyche. Through a combination of photography and AI-generated details, this series of image manipulations explores the surreal world of the mind. Through a decade of self-reflection and observation, the artist seeks to uncover human behaviors and how they assimilate in today's environment. The discoveries became the central part of the story. Step through the gate and explore a unique and fascinating perspective on reality.
